data.value: A deep statistical tool that would show important statistics from your daily social activity seems to be missing from the internet right now. The reason is pretty obvious, no one is willing to trust his/her private discussions to a third party. At this time, people are not comfortable on downloading softwares outside a trusted web store fearing of malware installations. What we do need is convincing people that open source projects have nothing to do with this.
